Package cetus.analysis

Class Relation

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.analysis.Relation
  • public class Relation
extends java.lang.Object
    Class Relation represents symbolic relationship between two expressions. The result of a symbolic comparison method in RangeDomain returns a Relation object.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor Description
      Relation()
      Constructs an empty relation that implies unknown relationship.
      Relation​(boolean lt, boolean eq, boolean gt)
      Constructs a relation object with the specified set of relationships.
